{"tid":939104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發新聞！！tumblr決定取消刪除色情內容！！！！！","createTime":"2018-12-13T00:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T16:18:29.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":112,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"05d1fee345b8735fe09052a8bfd3052b2e1ec2c2","tid":939104,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:02:14.000Z","msg":"The frantic, unprecedented race to save 700,000 NSFW Tumblrs for posterity<br />\nVolunteers are scrambling to download up to 800 terabytes of content from Tumblr&rsquo;s adult-themed community before it disappears from view on December 17.<br />\n<br />\nThe frantic, unprecedented race to save 700,000 NSFW Tumblrs for posterity<br />\nBY SEAN CAPTAIN5 MINUTE READ<br />\nGeoCities, Vine, Friendster&ndash;communities live, thrive, and often die on the net. But the two-week timeframe in which content will disappear from Tumblr is unprecedented, says Jason Scott. He cofounded Archive Team, a volunteer project running software that scarfs copies of endangered websites for posterity.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThey are now scrambling to preserve an estimated 700,000 Tumblr blogs that are expected to partly or entirely disappear due to a new, broadly defined ban on &ldquo;adult content&rdquo; announced on December 3. That makes Monday the 17th D-Day, when images, GIFs, and videos flagged as verboten by Tumblr&rsquo;s AI will disappear from public view&ndash;and probably from the reach of archivists.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Usually we&rsquo;re given 30 or 60 days or 90 days warning. Fourteen days is insane,&rdquo; says Scott. &ldquo;So we&rsquo;re going to probably get just a percentage. Frankly, I don&rsquo;t know what that percentage is.&rdquo; For comparison, the team has mostly finished archiving GeoCities Japan, which won&rsquo;t go offline until March 2019.<br />\n<br />\nOther people are also offering tools to preserve these blogs, but not at the industrial scale of the Archive Team effort&ndash;which may still not be enough."},{"pid":"c699a44ccfb483ad9743a7dbca3132c0f2060eff","tid":939104,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:02:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.fastcompany.com/90279321/the-frantic-unprecedented-race-to-save-700000-nsfw-tumblr-for-posterity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fastcompany.com%2F90279321%2Fthe-frantic-unprecedented-race-to-save-700000-nsfw-tumblr-for-posterity&d=hc3C8GZ198Ygz40kVha4nV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=028bda6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fastcompany.com/90279321/the-frantic-unprecedented-race-to-save-700000-nsfw-tumblr-for-posterity</a>"},{"pid":"0509f7c6741e6e11f9145bdf78c3414bf719f8e3","tid":939104,"uid":172844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bafb57c58659b7828eb133ebdff968edc0a9ecf","tid":939104,"uid":163350,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:03:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18c079b64fec89426e917f33568c7e326d92dcb5","tid":939104,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":156,"score":-155,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:04:06.000Z","msg":"<code>Xboxone Contana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"c73c86e924e6201f4cc2ec6fb96a51a3dea70ca8","tid":939104,"uid":12021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:04:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"798a831d3e798662c4f041bd07b779573acc98b6","tid":939104,"uid":15696,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:05:57.000Z","msg":"識唔識英文？"},{"pid":"448e7482990992276051d8cd0e16ef59ad13f7e6","tid":939104,"uid":5547,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:07:10.000Z","msg":"頂你唔識英文就咪post亂post啦 <img src=\"/ass